        "subject": "=Freedom of Information Act / RTI Request — {{ $('Webhook — Receive FOIA Request').item.json.body.request_id }}",
        "message": "=<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p><p>Please find below a formal public records request submitted under the applicable freedom of information / right to information statute for your jurisdiction.</p><p><strong>Request ID:</strong> {{ $('Webhook — Receive FOIA Request').item.json.body.request_id }}<br><strong>Agency:</strong> {{ $('Webhook — Receive FOIA Request').item.json.body.agency_name }}<br><strong>Jurisdiction:</strong> {{ $('Webhook — Receive FOIA Request').item.json.body.jurisdiction }}<br><strong>Date Sent:</strong> {{ $('Webhook — Receive FOIA Request').item.json.body.date_sent }}<br><strong>Response Due:</strong> {{ $('Webhook — Receive FOIA Request').item.json.body.response_due }}</p><hr><pre>{{ $('Webhook — Receive FOIA Request').item.json.body.letter_text }}</pre><hr><p>This request was generated by the FOIA/RTI Request Generator on behalf of {{ $('Webhook — Receive FOIA Request').item.json.body.requester_name }}.</p><p>Please direct any correspondence regarding this request to the contact details provided in the letter above.</p>",
