        "subject": "Follow-Up: Outstanding FOIA/RTI Request — {{ $json['Request ID'] }}",
        "message": "=<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p><p>I am writing to follow up on my public records request submitted on <strong>{{ $json['Date Sent'] }}</strong> (Request ID: <strong>{{ $json['Request ID'] }}</strong>).</p><p>As of today, the statutory response deadline of <strong>{{ $json['Response Due'] }}</strong> has passed, and I have not yet received a response or acknowledgment of my request.</p><p><strong>Request Details:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Request ID:</strong> {{ $json['Request ID'] }}</li><li><strong>Agency:</strong> {{ $json['Agency Name'] }}</li><li><strong>Jurisdiction:</strong> {{ $json['Jurisdiction'] }}</li><li><strong>Subject:</strong> {{ $json['Subject'] }}</li><li><strong>Original Date Sent:</strong> {{ $json['Date Sent'] }}</li><li><strong>Response Due:</strong> {{ $json['Response Due'] }}</li></ul><p>I respectfully request that you process this request at your earliest convenience and provide the requested records or a written explanation for any delay or denial.</p><p>Please contact me if you need any additional information to locate the requested records.</p><p>Thank you for your attention to this matter.</p><p>Sincerely,<br>{{ $json['Requester Name'] }}</p><hr><p style='color: #666; font-size: 12px;'>This is an automated follow-up sent by the FOIA/RTI Request Generator.</p>",
